{"tid":1634983,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有城邦論 沒有今日運動","createTime":"2019-10-07T11:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T14:08:20.000Z","uid":157994,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a6aa421965ed0f1819feabf4271e0e45932024","tid":1634983,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"知你班偽獨一定會還拖，屌定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F2mPRgT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF2mPRgT.jpg&h=112ca71d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果無城邦論，就唔會有勇武，無快樂抗爭，無反東北，無雨傘革命，無魚蛋革命，更唔會催生到今日既維權衛法運動<br />\n<br />\n陳雲自2014以來，已經每日唸經寫文，超渡眾生、廣傳知識，每一日都係為緊香港自治出力，無奈你地全部人都淨係識食玩訓，去到今日，老師既1234, 已經比你班偽獨做到12345678，偽獨更騎劫運動，不願叫老師的口號，反而追隨新泛民梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n狗眼看人低的香港人<br />\n你地必遭天罰<br />\n城邦派會記住你地點對老師"},{"pid":"91ed3c4b26606b2af0d0f22b8cf6834daad4d556","tid":1634983,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"食咗藥就係老師，未食藥仲要幫佢執手尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f96abb8ed42bc824d3be94c1bf229eda4da4b1","tid":1634983,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:44:47.000Z","msg":"無論食唔食藥都係神經病一個<br />\n信徙彈開d"},{"pid":"50f720fa15684f13b4560ee8f2dba1939de617b9","tid":1634983,"uid":282535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"陳雲勇武咗去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b929cce330d209be783d92492ba38288abcf1b45","tid":1634983,"uid":188511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"今時今日 陳雲都依然咁厚面皮扮大台<br />\n原來選舉近了 不推文回覆"},{"pid":"e20a41e71b77f68258729a8fa856dd1e82cd6155","tid":1634983,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"城邦派只智取，不胡亂勇武"},{"pid":"3917a80d4e01bd98ce58dbd938